-- Turkey's Halkbank says appoints new chief executive
-- 
-- Sat Feb 08, 2014 10:56AM EST
-- None



ISTANBUL, Feb 8 (Reuters) - Turkish state-run lender Halkbank <HALKB.IS> has appointed Ali Fuat Taskesenlioglu as chief executive, the bank said late on Friday, after the previous head of the bank was detained last month in connection with a corruption enquiry.

